'''Mohamed Beltagy''' is an Egyptian [[Muslim Brotherhood]] parliamentarian.<ref>[http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/06/08/us-egypt-rafah-border-idUSTRE65733Q20100608 Egypt lets Muslim Brotherhood MPs into Gaza]</ref>
He was on board the ''Mavi Marmara'' during the [[Gaza flotilla raid]].<ref>[http://www.thedailynewsegypt.com/people/muslim-brotherhood-mp-recounts-his-experience-on-freedom-flotilla-dp1.html Muslim Brotherhood MP recounts his experience on freedom flotilla]</ref>
